Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:05.91,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:122039,125917}The National Acting Contest\Nhas finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:125917,128670}May and the crew try their best\Nto win first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:12.15,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:128670,132150}However, on their performance day, through a conspiracy by Onodera…
