Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.85,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:134551,136854}What's worse, the rest of the crew\Nwho went to get the substitute equipment…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:20.39,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:136854,140390}…couldn't come back on time for their performance.
