Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161370,162787}Maya. Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164498,165707}They're not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165707,167459}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167459,168543}Tsukikage-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169920,171672}We cannot wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171672,173090}You have to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173090,174424}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176259,178345}You have to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179221,180221}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181765,183183}There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183183,184059}Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185143,185977}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187688,189314}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189314,190565}I'll get on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190565,191483}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.11,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:191483,193110}– No way!\N– That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193110,194861}Please let me do it, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194861,197364}I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197364,200951}Even though I might not be successful,\NI cannot give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200951,203829}I want to bet on every slight possibility we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203829,206707}You'll do it?\NBut all by yourself, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209834,211253}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217926,224908}{\an8}"Gena and the Five Blue Pots"\Nby Tsukikage Theater is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223765,225442}What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224908,228060}{\an8}Play time is one hour and forty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246830,249624}Good bye, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249624,250458}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250458,254045}I'll house sit till tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254045,256130}I won't let any strangers in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257924,260510}Wait a minute, something is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260510,261928}Father's words were skipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266433,267808}I wonder who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270771,271521}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272647,273690}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273690,275442}Oh, a traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275817,278987}Wearing a hood all over your head,\Nand look at how dirty you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278987,281490}Sorry, but I can't let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281490,282157}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282157,283366}You're being chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283366,285827}You want me to keep the blue pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285827,287454}Well, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287454,288663}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288663,289247}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289247,290540}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290540,293418}I won't open the lid of the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293418,294920}No, I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294920,298089}Excuse me, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298089,300008}I guess I have to accept it…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303595,306348}What a silly girl,\Ntrying to act all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306348,308475}{\i1}But she'll soon make some mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308475,310644}{\i1}She can't continue on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310644,312354}Look, I see some horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312354,315690}They are the three Princes\Nfrom the Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315690,316399}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316399,318151}On this pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318151,321238}There's a family mark hidden on this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321238,324199}…and they'll take over the neighboring country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324199,324991}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324991,326618}Oh, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326618,328245}Please don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328245,330789}I don't know anything about a man with a pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330789,331998}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331998,333583}I will never say anything about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333583,335877}So please, take the sword off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338839,341967}Rei. I don't think they can fix the truck anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341967,343051}I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343051,345178}Let's walk to a nearby town where we can make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348682,349349}Rei…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349349,349808}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349808,351852}I wonder what happened to our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354229,357357}We just have to hurry up and contact Tsukikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364155,366198}Y-Yes, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366867,368243}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368243,369536}Oh, Sheriff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369536,370996}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370996,374040}There's no one else but her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374040,375500}But it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375500,377836}Hey, I heard in the lobby…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377836,380881}Apparently everyone else is missing but her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380881,382591}Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382591,383550}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383550,384718}Something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384718,386720}The Princess came first, and now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386720,389472}{\i1}I can't believe she's getting on the stage all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389472,392349}Okay, I'll let you know if I hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394019,395061}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395478,399024}{\i1}And she's making sense\Nof it as a play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399608,400734}{\i1}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400317,402986}{\an8}A team of two is after this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404195,405322}No, I can't report it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405322,407657}It would be fine if there's jewelry inside…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407657,409743}But if it's really\Nthe Mark of the Royal Family…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409743,413163}And they find out that it was me who turned it in to the Sheriff…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413163,414414}They'll kill me for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414414,416499}{\i1}What lively acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416499,419878}{\i1}She doesn't even look like the same girl as the one crying in the rain back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421212,422881}Now what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422881,426384}There are four groups looking for this pot,\Nevery one for different things inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426384,429429}The Princess from the Castle…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429429,431473}The Sheriff…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431473,436478}The snake dancer who is looking for a venomous snake…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436478,440106}And the Queen\Nwho is looking for a love potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440649,443109}I wonder what in the world\Ncould it be in this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443109,445195}Should I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445195,449698}It might even be none of those four,\Nbut something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453828,455455}Maybe a venomous snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461920,463338}A mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463338,464422}You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464422,465048}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465048,467092}I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470053,471554}I'm so sorry, Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472639,476058}The truck broke down on the way back,\Nand we finally walked to this town nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477435,478937}W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478937,481189}They play is on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481189,482232}All by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482232,482941}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482941,484442}She's playing all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484442,485694}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485694,488613}The lady next door saw this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488613,492283}She'll tell everyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492283,496955}Then everyone will come looking for this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496955,501459}But I have to keep the promise I made with the traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505797,507340}Scene change.\NHurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507340,508049}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508049,508675}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508675,510467}Are they back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510467,511010}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511010,512595}I don't think they'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514014,515557}I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516850,521896}I never heard of anyone acting a play one hour and forty minutes long all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521896,526818}But the audience is getting more and more into it, and she doesn't bore us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527819,531364}She's doing good so far, but she can't make it through the last half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531364,535910}What is she going to do with the scene where everyone comes into the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548923,550050}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550050,552302}This way no one can get in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552302,553511}Oh, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558516,561853}I painted all the pots blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561853,566775}The only pot that's not blue\Nis this brown one with clay on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566775,568775}I hope they won't know this is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571738,574699}Oh, the Princess from the Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574699,575992}Sorry, but I can't open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578703,583208}What are you going to do\Nif you break in and find nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583208,585960}Here, which blue pot are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585960,588171}This one has pickles in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588171,590131}This one has rotten grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590131,592425}Can you smell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592425,596096}And… this one has ashes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597931,599182}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599182,601309}My hands slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601309,602602}Oh, you're going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605939,609483}{\i1}Maya is playing all by herself.\NI can't believe it. How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620662,623748}Oh, warriors from the Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623748,624457}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624457,627836}You arrested the three rulers who came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627836,629838}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629838,631631}What's in the blue pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631631,633800}Then, you must be from the Royal Family…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633800,635260}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635260,639556}She's the only one on the stage,\Nbut I can almost see the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639556,642350}I don't know anything about a pot with a venomous snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643351,645520}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645520,648148}There's no one else on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648148,650233}But no one even cares about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650233,651442}Yes, Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651442,653611}I don't have a pot with a love potion in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653611,656447}All I have is one with centipedes and bird droppings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656948,660160}Oh, she left feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660535,663496}Oh, you found the one with the venomous snake in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663496,665665}Good for you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665665,666749}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666749,668668}Be careful with the snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682223,684058}Yes, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684058,686310}Oh? You're from Sheriff's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687437,691482}You arrested the murderer\Nwho stole the jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691482,692942}You found the pot, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692942,694485}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694485,695862}You just came to let me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695862,696945}Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703369,708666}I guess no one is looking\Nfor this pot after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709584,711500}It'll get harder from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711500,713963}The climax scene where the jewel thief appears.
Comment: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:23.99,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:743993,743993}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:27.74,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:747747,747747}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:30.75,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:750750,750750}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782782,785243}All the lids of the pots are opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785243,786953}I don't remember opening them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786953,788953}Besides, they're all\Nin different places!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788953,789789}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789789,791582}The lamp I put here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795252,796045}Who…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796045,797130}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797130,799090}Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802302,804137}How did you get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804137,805430}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807890,809100}Don't stay silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809100,810685}Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820695,821779}That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821779,823656}Let me go! Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835376,836794}It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836794,838129}Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838129,841716}You are the one who came to say\Nyou arrested the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841716,843009}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843009,846262}You are the murderer the Sheriff is looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848348,849932}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854896,855605}Someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855605,857690}Help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857690,858900}Oh, the traveler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858900,860568}Please catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866407,867617}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867617,869869}This man is a thief and a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869869,871746}Here, I'll go get some rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873081,874290}Oh, Sheriff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874290,876166}We caught the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880003,883841}He told me that he buried the pot he stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883841,886344}He told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886344,887970}Here, Mr. Traveler…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887970,890390}Tell me, what's in this pot I protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893517,896062}What? Just some apple sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896062,899482}What about that you were chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899482,900608}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900608,902777}By a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902777,905321}You came to the city to work, but were unsuccessful…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905321,910993}…and you are taking this jar back for your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910993,912703}Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913329,914997}Oh, it's all bright already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914997,917834}I can't believe all that happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930138,932265}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932265,933641}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933641,935641}How was work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935641,939939}You have so much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939939,941858}You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941858,944026}I'll fix you breakfast right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976476,978766}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978766,980938}You gave your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980938,983357}The audience can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983357,985860}Here, go greet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985860,987361}Greet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987361,988488}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988488,989738}Here, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996496,998664}Look at her, she's really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998664,1001291}What a difference from the composure\Nshe had when she was on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001959,1004002}{\i1}Otto-san, Keiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004002,1006297}{\i1}You two saved this play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006297,1007131}{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015723,1017098}{\i1}She looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024106,1027401}I worried how it would be without us, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027401,1029570}She's a total genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029570,1033241}She's just a normal girl off stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041457,1046045}The National Acting Contest is now over…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046045,1049131}…and the judges are making their decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049131,1055137}While we await,\Nhere's the vote from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056889,1058015}Third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058015,1060601}Ondine from Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060601,1061602}"The Castle of Ashes".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061602,1062770}Third place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062770,1064021}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064021,1065356}Second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065356,1068276}Ikkakuju Theater from Hokkaidō.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068276,1069026}"Destiny".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068609,1069610}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069610,1071320}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071320,1072947}And first place goes to…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072947,1075283}Tsukikage Theater from Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075283,1077284}"Gena and the Five Blue Pots".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080079,1081664}Wow, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081664,1082498}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082498,1083583}You were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083583,1084792}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084792,1087086}{\i1}The audience chose her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087086,1090715}{\i1}The girl who was looking over our practice last year through the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091799,1094343}The audience doesn't know anything about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094343,1096178}What matters is the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099056,1100975}What's wrong, Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100975,1102976}We were chosen for first place\Nby the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104353,1107315}We'll make it to second\Nor third place at the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107315,1108691}I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108691,1111652}We might not be chosen for a prize by the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111652,1113070}T-Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113070,1115656}The judges have made their decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116407,1117575}Let's see the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120536,1121454}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123121,1127877}I want to comment before the final announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127877,1130630}W-What are you doing, Onodera-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130630,1133424}First of all, Tsukikage Theater's\N"Gene and the Five Blue Pots"…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133424,1137053}…is far from the true spirit of acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140222,1144894}As you can see in the script, it was supposed to be ten people on the stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144894,1148147}…but there was only one that stood on the stage in actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148147,1151817}The rest did not show up without the permission of your committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151817,1154737}Therefore, they should not be judged on the same ground…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155863,1158574}…so I ask you to reconsider the judging again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160618,1163371}– You know how persistent Onodera-san is.\N– I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164497,1165706}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165706,1166874}There was a reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166874,1168459}The reason doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168459,1172169}What's important is that you missed this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173172,1174340}Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174340,1176634}The main actor not only changed her words in various ways…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176634,1179512}…she played in her own selfish way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181055,1184975}We will reconsider\Nthe decisions by the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184975,1186476}It'll be announced in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188312,1191023}I can't believe such an irrational thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191023,1191941}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191941,1194402}What's wrong with an actor trying her best?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194402,1195695}There's solo play in acting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202493,1203911}Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203911,1206580}We will now announce the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207581,1209041}Third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209041,1211252}Hagi Theater from Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211252,1212461}"Dead End".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212461,1213629}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213629,1215297}Hagi Theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216465,1218300}They were voted for\Nthe 5th place by the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218300,1219385}Second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219385,1221804}Ikkakuju Theater from Hokkaidō.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221804,1222722}"Destiny".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224682,1226600}And the first place goes to…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228894,1232440}…Ondine Theater from Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232440,1233816}"The Castle of Ashes".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233816,1235317}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237445,1239610}What happened to Tsukikage Theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240947,1245202}Uh, Tsukikage Theater's\N"Gena and the Five Blue Pots"…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245202,1251041}…was disqualified due to its lack\Nin following the true spirit of acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255421,1256172}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256172,1258674}You did all you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260384,1262678}Yes. You gave your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262678,1264638}But… But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264638,1266432}Would you like my handkerchief, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271520,1272563}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272563,1276901}Gena, who fought a thief in the dark, is crying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279111,1282823}I'll never use your handkerchief, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282823,1285451}So what if you're the president of Metropolitan Entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285451,1286577}I won't kiss ass like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286577,1288037}Maya, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288037,1290414}You'll be okay with that kind of attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291415,1294293}Too bad, though you tried all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295461,1297004}Silence, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298130,1299465}Ayumi-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299465,1303052}I'm looking forward to competing with you on stage at the next competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303052,1305095}I won't lose next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307515,1308682}Ayumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308682,1310726}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310726,1312645}We're the ones who won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312645,1316564}I don't think I lost in terms of acting…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317650,1320611}…but I have this feeling of defeat in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320611,1321904}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321904,1324281}You lost the competition,\Nbut best of luck to you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324281,1325574}I liked your Gena so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325574,1327576}You did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327576,1330329}The audience chose her acting out of their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332122,1334250}We lost to her in a sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334250,1336710}Even though they've forgotten our play…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1336710,1339964}…her play will always live in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340965,1342132}Anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342132,1345386}It's a fact that she played for one hour and forty minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345386,1349056}…all by herself and was chosen for first place by the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354395,1355729}Tsukikage-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355729,1357940}Now that you didn't win first prize…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357940,1363863}…we, Aoyagi Productions,\Nhave to take your house and property.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363863,1364780}Understood?
Comment: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:51.41,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1371412,1371412}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:04.88,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1378750,1384880}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.88,0:23:10.97,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384880,1390970}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:22.98,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1390970,1402980}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:35.12,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1402980,1415120}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:41.00,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1415120,1421000}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:47.13,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1421000,1427130}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.13,0:23:53.22,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1427130,1433220}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.22,0:23:59.31,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1433220,1439310}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:05.32,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1439310,1445320}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:11.28,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1445320,1451280}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
