Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:27.63,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1464588,1467633}After disqualification from the National Contest, Tsukikage Theater's troupe…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.63,0:24:31.80,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1467633,1471804}…borrows a small apartment and starts a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.80,0:24:36.93,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1471804,1476934}Soon enough, Maya receives\Nan invitation to Theater Ondine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:41.02,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1476934,1481021}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Masumi's Passion".
